Expenses per day trends

Let's start by adding some money to your wallet.

Click "Add Profit" button and fill the form in modal window. It's simple. You can also set current total with "Set Total To" dialog.

We don't ask you to track every transaction you've done(though you can). Feel free to update your DimeShift wallet every evening, or even once in few days.

Click "set total to" action link and fill the form to check how it works. It's time to add some expense.

You can add transaction with one string, e.g. "99.93, best expense ever".
